              "type": "text",
              "id": "SxpjR",
              "name": "missionBody",
              "fill": "#888898",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 800,
              "content": "Singapore's car market is one of the most regulated in the world — with COE bidding, PARF rebates, and registration quotas shaping every purchase decision. Yet finding clear, consolidated data has always been a challenge.\n\nMotorMetrics was built to change that. We aggregate data from LTA DataMall and present it through interactive charts, trend analysis, and AI-powered insights — making it easier for buyers, sellers, and enthusiasts to understand the market.",
